my care. You'll just corrupt him!

35
00:03:35,768 --> 00:03:38,453
Get away from her!

36
00:03:39,032 --> 00:03:41,404
Stop that! What are you doing to the poor thing?

37
00:03:42,546 --> 00:03:46,020
Ahh! Come on! I'm getting stung like crazy here!

38
00:03:46,045 --> 00:03:49,577
Quit it! Can't you see you're hurting him?
You're gonna pull his arm out of the socket!

39
00:03:49,602 --> 00:03:53,102
You think he's hurting, look at
me! I'm getting seriously stung!

40
00:03:57,044 --> 00:03:59,439
Jeez! Are you crazy? What's your problem?

41
00:03:59,464 --> 00:04:02,747
I told you! When he has naughty
thoughts, I'm the one who pays for it.

42
00:04:02,772 --> 00:04:04,620
Every one of 'em stings me!

43
00:04:05,739 --> 00:04:07,261
What do you mean naughty thoughts?

44
00:04:07,286 --> 00:04:10,677
Ugh, please! You were just
talking about him living with you.

45
00:04:10,790 --> 00:04:14,503
At his age, that's basically guaranteeing
a whole crap ton of dirty thoughts!

46
00:04:14,528 --> 00:04:17,219
The answer is no! He'll be staying with me!

47
00:04:17,520 --> 00:04:20,683
You know, I think it's really someone
else who has his mind in the gutter.

48
00:04:21,175 --> 00:04:26,425
Unlike you, he's a good boy. There's nothing
to worry about. Now, come with me, Yukine.

49
00:04:26,727 --> 00:04:28,616
