52
00:04:47,911 --> 00:04:50,978
Don't be silly. I'm just an ordinary teenager.

53
00:04:51,994 --> 00:04:57,335
Yeah, well, this doesn't look very ordinary
to me. Are your parents around here somewhere?

54
00:04:58,501 --> 00:05:01,895
We got lucky. It looks like
they're actually out late tonight.

55
00:05:02,102 --> 00:05:04,903
Huh? You mean it's just you and
me? We have the whole place to our...

56
00:05:04,928 --> 00:05:07,327
oh, no! Sh!

57
00:05:09,416 --> 00:05:11,264
Ah, I thought I heard you, Hiyori.

58
00:05:11,289 --> 00:05:13,051
Yeah, it's me, Sasaki.

59
00:05:13,734 --> 00:05:15,376
Nice evening, isn't it?

60
00:05:18,804 --> 00:05:22,558
I have a bath drawn for you. Feel free
to hop in whenever you're ready, dear!

61
00:05:34,343 --> 00:05:36,732
Whoa! This is awesome!

62
00:05:37,359 --> 00:05:39,994
Go ahead and make yourself at home you can stay in here.

63
00:05:40,308 --> 00:05:42,854
