64
00:05:42,879 --> 00:05:45,049
No. It's my big brother's.

65
00:05:45,247 --> 00:05:46,232
Your brother?

66
00:05:46,654 --> 00:05:48,703
Yeah. He's a lot older than me.

67
00:05:49,306 --> 00:05:51,975
He doesn't live here anymore, so the room's all yours.

68
00:05:54,185 --> 00:05:55,201
Oh, okay.

69
00:05:55,624 --> 00:05:57,386
It's great. If you're sure.

70
00:05:58,207 --> 00:06:00,167
I'm not far. My room's next door.

71
00:06:00,461 --> 00:06:03,876
Let me know if you need anything. Well, see you in a bit!

72
00:06:12,510 --> 00:06:15,310
Looks like Hiyori's really living a dream life, isn't she?

73
00:06:20,172 --> 00:06:26,532
Everything went as planned. We made a stealthy
entrance, unnoticed by our housekeeper or my parents.

74
00:06:26,557 --> 00:06:28,017
Oh! Hi, you guys!

75
00:06:28,042 --> 00:06:29,631
Surprise! We're early!

76
00:06:29,656 --> 00:06:32,195
Lookie! We brought home a tasty snack!

77
00:06:32,600 --> 00:06:36,425
Well. I think I'll have a
nightcap if it's okay with you, dear.

78
00:06:36,584 --> 00:06:39,043
Oh! You're absolutely incorrigible!

79
00:06:45,912 --> 00:06:48,728
This is the best part of my
day! And now for a little snack.

80
00:06:48,753 --> 00:06:52,125
Don't eat too much, now. Have you washed your hands, dear?

81
00:06:57,732 --> 00:07:01,615
