83
00:07:03,981 --> 00:07:06,936
Your mom sure doesn't miss much, does she?

84
00:07:07,269 --> 00:07:09,819
What are you doing here? This is my house!

85
00:07:09,844 --> 00:07:13,304
Jeez what's the big deal? It's not
like they're gonna notice that I'm here.

86
00:07:13,329 --> 00:07:16,535
The whole point was to separate
Yukine from your bad influence!

87
00:07:17,952 --> 00:07:20,503
Speaking of, how's he taking it so far?

88
00:07:21,778 --> 00:07:23,774
How do you think? He's thrilled, of course!

89
00:07:23,870 --> 00:07:27,692
Do you think he really enjoys sleeping in a
different, random shrine every night with you?

90
00:07:28,399 --> 00:07:32,284
Unlike this house, shrine grounds
and buildings are sacred territory.

91
00:07:32,378 --> 00:07:35,045
Which means they keep US safe from phantom attacks.

92
00:07:35,659 --> 00:07:36,738
Even so.

93
00:07:37,138 --> 00:07:41,967
Haven't you ever heard that things go bump in
the night? That's the phantoms' favorite time.

94
00:07:42,461 --> 00:07:45,656
