107
00:08:37,049 --> 00:08:39,831
Did Hiyori just take a bath in this water, too?

108
00:08:45,304 --> 00:08:48,275
Ah! Here you are. I've been looking for you.

109
00:08:48,497 --> 00:08:52,564
Hey, Hiyori! I found what I needed! Don't worry about it!

110
00:08:56,247 --> 00:09:01,376
