121
00:09:35,202 --> 00:09:37,135
hurry up already, it's getting cold.

122
00:09:37,160 --> 00:09:40,318
B-b-b-b-but I!

123
00:09:44,740 --> 00:09:48,121
Yeah, it's been a while since I slept with someone, too.

124
00:09:50,362 --> 00:09:53,825
You don't smell like a boy. You smell nice.

125
00:09:55,031 --> 00:09:58,119
I like this. Lying next to someone.

126
00:09:58,480 --> 00:09:59,577
It's soothing.

127
00:10:00,396 --> 00:10:03,176
It's kinda nice not to be alone at night, you know?

128
00:10:36,554 --> 00:10:39,808
Young man, just what do you think you're doing?

129
00:10:44,584 --> 00:10:47,118
You jerk! What are you doing here?

130
00:10:47,261 --> 00:10:50,185
Don't give me that, you little
punk! What were you about to do?

131
00:10:50,424 --> 00:10:51,577
No, I...

132
00:10:51,836 --> 00:10:53,937
listen, Hiyori said I could be there!

133
00:10:54,942 --> 00:10:59,388
You're not ready to have girls in your
life yet. So behave. For now, I'm all you need.

134
00:10:59,607 --> 00:11:02,180
When you say stuff like that, it makes me wanna puke.

135
00:11:02,649 --> 00:11:06,995
And anyway, you've got a girl. A
regalia like me, but she's a chick.

136
00:11:08,355 --> 00:11:10,372
So what do you even need me for?

137
00:11:22,638 --> 00:11:24,515
Gonna be another stormy night.

138
00:11:41,464 --> 00:11:43,936
Closing in on downtown. Location reached.

139
00:11:45,757 --> 00:11:47,280
Incoming: Six o'clock!

140
00:12:02,837 --> 00:12:03,708
We're done here.

141
00:12:10,401 --> 00:12:12,321
I'm glad you came. This is fun.

142
00:12:13,964 --> 00:12:15,971
Didn't have anything else to do, so.

143
00:12:17,452 --> 00:12:19,090
Those look nice. You want a pair?

144
00:12:19,204 --> 00:12:19,941
Uhh...

145
00:12:20,091 --> 00:12:21,950
It is getting colder outside.

146
00:12:22,235 --> 00:12:23,824
Let's see how much I have.

147
00:12:23,849 --> 00:12:26,565
No! It's okay. I don't need anything, I promise.

148
00:12:26,590 --> 00:12:28,789
Oh, come on. I want to get them for you.

149
00:12:28,814 --> 00:12:34,952
But I'm fine, really! I mean, it's not like anyone can see
me, right? So, if I want something, I can just borrow it.

150
00:12:44,866 --> 00:12:49,893
Hey! You should know better than that!
What you're doing's no different than stealing!

151
00:12:49,918 --> 00:12:52,316
What? I said I'm just borrowing it.

152
00:12:52,485 --> 00:12:53,341
I'll give it right back.

153
00:12:53,366 --> 00:12:56,461
Well, it's still wrong. Here, give it to me.

154
00:13:02,781 --> 00:13:06,395
The next time you want something
like this, just tell me okay?

155
00:13:08,796 --> 00:13:09,970
Where did he go?

156
00:13:10,804 --> 00:13:11,367
Hey.

157
00:13:14,426 --> 00:13:16,904
Yato? What are you doing here?

158
00:13:16,929 --> 00:13:19,925
Getting a little r and r. I'm not feeling so good today.

159
00:13:21,116 --> 00:13:23,648
You are looking after him like you said, aren't you?

160
00:13:24,069 --> 00:13:26,188
'Cause it seems like he's been gettin' in trouble.

161
00:13:27,172 --> 00:13:29,044
