181
00:15:29,458 --> 00:15:32,869
I screwed up. I wonder if she's still mad at me.

182
00:15:35,656 --> 00:15:37,288
Crap! It's that late?

183
00:15:46,623 --> 00:15:47,373
Damn it!

184
00:15:48,861 --> 00:15:50,309
Hurry!

185
00:15:54,307 --> 00:15:56,549
Faster! I hate the dark!

186
00:15:56,583 --> 00:15:57,856
I'm scared.

187
00:15:59,840 --> 00:16:00,924
It's dark.

188
00:16:02,829 --> 00:16:08,061
I don't like the dark. Mommy. Please come and get me!

189
00:16:11,539 --> 00:16:13,947
You stopped walking. You can see me?

190
00:16:16,280 --> 00:16:17,171
Oh no.

191
00:16:21,453 --> 00:16:26,480
You can see me! Everybody else out here just ignores me!

192
00:16:26,638 --> 00:16:31,162
Well, these eyeball things try to
talk to me, but they're weird and scary.

193
00:16:32,158 --> 00:16:33,468
This girl...

194
00:16:34,029 --> 00:16:42,549
I'm waiting for my mommy, just like I'm supposed to.
She comes to pick me up after my tutoring session is over.

195
00:16:43,035 --> 00:16:45,280
Oh, she does, huh?

196
00:16:45,305 --> 00:16:49,153
She shouldn't be much longer.
Will you please wait here with me?

197
00:16:49,312 --> 00:16:50,934
Just 'til six o'clock.

198
00:16:54,495 --> 00:16:55,253
Sure.

199
00:16:59,715 --> 00:17:01,073
Where is he?

200
00:17:05,029 --> 00:17:11,352
I'm really sorry. I guess my mommy's running late.
Your family's probably worried about you, too, huh?

201
00:17:11,511 --> 00:17:14,586
Family? I don't really have one of those.

202
00:17:17,375 --> 00:17:21,860
Hey, I know! When my mommy gets here,
you can come home with US too, okay?

203
00:17:21,957 --> 00:17:26,818
Don't worry. I'm sure she'll get here soon. Really.

204
00:17:29,344 --> 00:17:31,655
No, she won't.

205
00:17:43,011 --> 00:17:45,120
Hey! Come back here!

206
00:17:45,153 --> 00:17:48,172
There you are! I've been looking everywhere for you!

207
