Wait, don't go that way!

208
00:17:49,832 --> 00:17:50,610
Huh?

209
00:17:50,744 --> 00:17:52,705
You must be so scared.

210
00:17:54,995 --> 00:18:05,844
Poor little girl... All lost and alone... in the dark.
But don't worry. It'll be okay. Your mommy is over here.

211
00:18:05,902 --> 00:18:07,253
My mommy?

212
00:18:07,278 --> 00:18:13,040
Come this way. Come to US.

213
00:18:13,498 --> 00:18:16,364
Yukine! Use that thing Yato taught you!

214
00:18:16,814 --> 00:18:19,248
First I have to make my hand into a halberd.

215
00:18:21,083 --> 00:18:21,782
Damn!

216
