228
00:19:40,028 --> 00:19:44,084
Boy smells nice. Mommy? Where?

229
00:19:46,198 --> 00:19:46,869
Yato!

230
00:19:46,894 --> 00:19:48,779
Yukine, you all right?

231
00:19:49,921 --> 00:19:53,901
That big phantom... A girl, went into it.

232
00:19:54,298 --> 00:19:55,355
Boy smells nice!

