00:20:17,890 --> 00:20:24,591
I now lay thee waste with the Sekki and
expel thy vast defilement. I cleanse thee.

238
00:20:28,766 --> 00:20:30,274
No! Yato!

239
00:20:33,403 --> 00:20:34,310
Stop!

240
00:20:34,485 --> 00:20:35,560
Rend!

241
00:20:42,237 --> 00:20:45,606
What the hell are you doing?
You were supposed to save her!

242
00:20:47,190 --> 00:20:51,045
It's too late for that. Can't you
see? She's been completely possessed!

243
00:20:51,070 --> 00:20:52,129
What are you saying?

244
00:20:52,154 --> 00:20:54,416
Killing her is the only choice we have now.

245
00:21:05,503 --> 00:21:06,452
Yukine.

246
00:21:07,143 --> 00:21:11,654
Once it has been corrupted and
consumed by a phantom, a soul is utterly lost.

247
00:21:11,761 --> 00:21:14,374
Its existence
can be nothing but a living hell!

248
00:21:18,338 --> 00:21:21,951
You must do this. Show her mercy and free her!

249
00:21:24,821 --> 00:21:25,904
Yukine!

250
00:21:30,369 --> 00:21:31,461
Rend!

251
00:22:05,077 --> 00:22:08,188
We've received word from
Kuraha, who's patrolling the city.

252
00:22:09,837 --> 00:22:12,377
It seems that he saw Yato, slaying a phantom.

253
00:22:14,255 --> 00:22:16,491
He appears to have obtained a new regalia.

254
00:22:17,672 --> 00:22:18,598
I see.

255
00:23:58,195 --> 00:24:00,719
How was your bath, Yukine? Nice and relaxing?

256
00:24:00,744 --> 00:24:04,994
Yeah. Oh, and I used some shampoo. I think it was
Rose-scented or something.

257
00:24:05,019 --> 00:24:06,465
I'm guessing it was yours, right?

258
00:24:06,580 --> 00:24:08,568
Actually, it's my dad's hair-growth cream.

259
00:24:08,593 --> 00:24:09,702
Your dad's?

260
00:24:09,727 --> 00:24:12,430
Next time on noragami: "Scary person."

